OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening but staying
OL,7,Fmostly cloudy with a few clear
OL,8,Fintervals breaking through. Dry
OL,9,Fovernight with some clear spells.
OL,10,FLight or moderate westerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FMainly dry with bright or
OL,13,Fsunny spells developing and feeling
OL,14,Fwarm in any sunshine. Winds light or
OL,15,Fmoderate from the southwest.
